            {
              "id": "516b494",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Hydrogen Production &amp; Dispensing Systems",
                "size": "xl",
                "align": "left",
                "header_size": "h2"
              },
              "elements": []
            },
            {
              "id": "6dcb786",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Harnessing cutting-edge electrolysis and blue hydrogen technologies with carbon capture, Amerigroup designs and deploys modular, scalable hydrogen production facilities.</p><p>Our hydrogen refueling stations are engineered for industrial, transportation, and power generation applications — empowering the shift toward a zero-carbon hydrogen economy.</p>"
              },
              "elements": []
            }
