              "elements": []
            },
            {
              "id": "f332ef6",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>With extensive experience in Mexico's energy sector, Amerigroup spearheads power grid modernization projects that incorporate advanced clean energy technologies.</p><p>Our services include integration of hydrogen and methanol fuel cells, renewables, and energy storage solutions into existing and new power plants.</p>"
