              "elements": []
            },
            {
              "id": "d0cd28d",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Amerigroup champions the electrification of transport through comprehensive e-mobility solutions — advanced EV fleets, commercial electric trucks, and hydrogen fuel cell vehicles.</p><p>Class 5 and 8 diesel-to-electric truck conversions with travel range up to 1,300 miles. Notable clients: Staples, UPS, FedEx, Kenworth.</p>"
