            {
              "id": "750c5f1",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Advanced Linear Generator Technology",
                "size": "xl",
                "align": "left",
                "header_size": "h2"
              },
              "elements": []
            },
            {
              "id": "9eb7fae",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Converts mechanical energy directly into electrical power with minimal moving parts. By employing a linear motion mechanism rather than traditional rotating components, this generator offers enhanced efficiency, longer operational lifespans, and greater reliability.</p>"
